data.description: Don’t miss out on this rare find in townhome floorplan that features the MASTER SUITE ON MAIN level!  Run, don’t walk to discover luxurious living in this almost new townhome with practical functionality.  This townhome is the one that keeps on giving as there is a loft and office space upstairs in addition to two guest bedrooms.  The main level features an open concept for the kitchen, dining and living rooms.  The upstairs loft can be an entertainment area, exercise haven or creative space while the office space will be perfect to work from home.  This townhome comes with a 2-car garage and back patio with privacy fences on the side. Don't miss your chance to call this incredible townhome yours! Schedule a showing today and unlock the door to a new chapter of luxury living. So, Welcome Home to Modern Elegance and Comfort! If listing broker shows first, buying broker commission will be reduced to 1% commission.
